parameters:
MasamuneIn order to proceed, we need to activate
this magic circle. What should we do?

In order to proceed through the dungeon, you need
to take Lesson 1 of Ritual Studies.

MasamuneThis seems to be one of the ritual
magic. It looks like it can be activated if done
like this.
particle play warp_red_cp player def above
particle play warp_red_cp player def above

MasamuneWhat's with that panda... hey, move
aside.

AmeliaYou're not moving. Maybe you're in a bad
mood.

AmeliaIf I give it my favorite bamboo rat, maybe
it will listen to me. It should be living
underground, so if we search, we might find it
here too, right?

MasamuneHow troublesome. Let's defeat it and
move forward.

AmeliaI remember that Hell Panda has a really
high magic resistance. Even we might end up
consuming quite a bit of magic power.

MasamuneI don't like that... Oh well, I guess
I'll try looking for a bamboo rat.

AmeliaI think if we give it about two, it will
be satisfied and listen to us. Its personality
should be gentle.
MasamuneLook, I brought a bamboo rat.
MasamuneShall we search for two bamboo rats?

Description MonkeyIt seems that there are floors
created with magic that allow you to jump high.
Don't be surprised and freak out all of a sudden.
Registered on the dungeon teleportation stone.
MasamuneThere's no need to use it now.
MasamuneShall we call it a day?
I'll finish up and return to my room

In the dungeon, you can end the day by using the
teleportation stone inside the dungeon. Also, when
you clear the dungeon, it becomes bedtime and the
day ends.
particle play warp_red_cp player def above

Is the dungeon over now? Please tell me the club
room is ahead.

It's rare to see you complain about something like
this.

Ugh... It's not a problem even if there's more to
come.

Monsters... And it seems like these are on a
different level than the ones we've fought so far.

To think that we have prepared a magic circle that
activates when intruders come.
I wonder how many things I don't want to be seen.

I can't believe there were even such violent
monsters. We had a bit of a tough fight.

I have plenty of experience fighting stronger
demons, you know.

Nevertheless, I can't believe we had monsters of
this level as part of our club activities.

On the contrary, I wonder if they are sealing
monsters that naturally spawn due to intense
magical power.
Perhaps the academy itself has that kind of role.

Living among monsters is dangerous, but
considering the position of a magician, it's
possible.

There's no way I would be defeated by such a weak
attack.

I nullified the magic attack just before it hit.
Not a scratch on me.
Well, there were some attacks that got through.
I'm sorry... It's because I let my guard down.

Thinking you've defeated them and letting your
guard down is absolutely something you should
never do.

Maybe I was a little too excited about my first
school life. Honestly, it was fun.
I failed as an older sister, huh...

I mean, I never thought of Amelia as my older
sister.
I'm no longer just someone who is protected.

I may still not be able to match Amelia, but I've
become strong enough, haven't I?

That's right. I've changed a lot since I joined
the team.
Ah... It's all for Amelia's sake.

(I have to do it now... It might not work, but at
least I have to make them aware)

I've always wanted to become someone who can
protect Amelia.

When I say 'I love you'... it's as a person of the
opposite sex...

Amelia might have thought of me as a younger
brother, but I've always been aware of her as the
opposite sex.

But it can't be helped. Amelia is cute and she
treats me kindly.

She might have treated me kindly out of sympathy,
but it made me incredibly happy.

I can't deny that there might have been some
sympathy, but it's not just that.

As we spent time together, Masamune-kun, who
became brighter, was cute.
(I guess there really are no romantic feelings...)
But, that was only in the beginning.
Masamune-kun, you're growing more and more...
It's natural because it's the growth period.

Of course. You have quite a muscular physique
compared to other people our age.

But, after training, you would walk around with
your upper body exposed.
That's because I take a shower right away.

But if I were to do it, Masamune-kun would get
excited, right?

(Amelia's breasts, I can use that as material for
a lifetime...)

I feel the same... If I were to see something like
that, I would become conscious...

So... does that mean you see me as the opposite
sex?
But you always see me as your little brother...

Otherwise, I wouldn't be able to interact with you
as my superior.

I'm glad you see me as a member of the opposite
sex.

So... even though it's a time like this, let me
say it.

I love you, Amelia... I want to be in a
relationship with you.

But, is it okay... we're in the middle of a
mission... and we're technically in a superior-
subordinate relationship.
I can't hold back my feelings for Amelia anymore.

I'm already filled with feelings of liking
Masamune.

If someone like me is okay... please take care of
me.
Wow... I never thought I would be confessed to.

That's because... until now, I didn't have any
rivals.

I was thinking that maybe someone at the academy
might take you away.
I'm not interested in anyone other than Masamune.
Yeah... even though we just kissed.

(The sensation of her lips still lingers... I want
to do more... ...but)
For now... should we move forward?

Amelia Hey, hey, is there any girl you're
interested in?
Masamune ...I like that kind of talk.

Masamune (Whenever I talk to other girls, she
immediately says something like this)

Masamune (She probably likes talking about
love... even though she doesn't seem interested in
it herself)

Amelia But you were talking to girls and getting
along with them, right?

Amelia Are you interested in Elena-chan? Or
maybe Hiyo-chan?
Amelia Ah, that gal-like girl was cute, right?

Masamune Even though we've only met for a few
days, I don't have the kind of feelings that
Amelia seems to be thinking about.

Masamune And besides, I'm not into gal-like
girls, you know.

Amelia I see. Then someone like Hiyo-chan would
be good, right? She had a gentle and refined vibe.

Masamune (Kuh, without even knowing my
feelings...)
Masamune Hiyo doesn't fit my taste either.
Amelia Hmm, then what kind of girl is your type?

Amelia Come to think of it, I've never heard
about that.

Masamune Well... I guess I prefer someone with a
more innocent vibe than a gal.
Amelia I-I didn't ask for that...
Amelia By the way, isn't that...

MasamuneThere are people in a place like this...
Could they be members of the Magic Research Club?

Sylvester von WeisshwaikIndeed, I am Sylvester
von Weisshwaik, a noble of the Kingdom of Prussia.

MasamuneNo, that doesn't matter. Sorry, but
could you pretend you didn't see anything?

Sylvester von WeisshwaikOh, if it isn't
unfamiliar faces. You all aren't members of the
Magic Research Club, are you?

Sylvester von WeisshwaikHowever, that doesn't
matter. Would you like to buy the magic potion I
developed?

Sylvester von WeisshwaikYou'll be amazed by how
incredible it is.
MasamuneI don't need any magic potion.

Sylvester von WeisshwaikHehehe... Do you all not
need any magic potions?
